import './App.css'

import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'
import NavBar from './Components/NavBar.jsx'
import AboutUs from './Components/AboutUs.jsx'
import ItemListContainer from './Container/ItemListContainer'
import Detalle from './Pages/Detalle.jsx'
import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from "react-router-dom"

function App() {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <NavBar />
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/" element={<ItemListContainer titulo='¡Bienvenido a Tienda Vapor!'/>} />
        <Route path="/about" element={<AboutUs />} />
        <Route path="/Atos" element={<ItemListContainer titulo='Atomizadores' filter='atos' key={randomGen()}/>} />
        <Route path="/Mods" element={<ItemListContainer titulo='Mods Electrónicos' filter='mods'/>} />
        <Route path="/Accesorios" element={<ItemListContainer titulo='Accesorios' filter='acc'/>} />
        <Route path="/Detalle" element={<Detalle />} />
      </Routes>  
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default App
